OL,5,G1100 The Fenn Street Gang
OL,6,     FPenny decides shes not staying at
OL,7,     Fhome, but has to hide her new job
OL,8,     Ffrom Bernard, whose views are very
OL,9,     Ftraditional. When he finally finds
OL,10,     Fwork, it unexpectedly puts him
OL,11,     Faround all kinds of people.
OL,12,G1130 Agony
OL,13,     FJane is stuck in the middle
OL,14,     Fbetween her friends. Rob moves out
OL,15,     Fto live with someone else who
OL,16,     Fturns out not to be gay. Michael
OL,17,     Fis outed by Jane's radio programme
OL,18,     Fand receives constant teasing at
OL,19,     Fwork
